news.title: Ludhiana civic body collects Rs 6 crore property tax on last day of rebate
news.para: On Friday, the civic officials mopped up Rs 6 crore. However, the collection amount is going to rise as officials are yet to include the recovery done by the field staff and the online payment which continues till midnight.

news.title: Coimbatore: Court relieves residents' association from clutches of promoter
news.para: There are 126 individual villas in the retirement community - Soundarayam And Santhosham. It came into existence in 2006. The size of each villa ranged from 1,000 sq ft to 3,000 sq ft.

news.title: Kanpur development body freezes rates of flats under its various schemes
news.para: According to KDA vice-chairman Arvind Singh KDA, it is an effort to give respite to citizens who are interested in having a flat in KDA schemes.
